  "synopsis": "Luke and Leia. The heroics of the Skywalker kids are lengendary thoughout the galaxy. Star Wars Tales #15 spotlights the adventures of the siblings through all manners of high adventure! Follow a young Luke as he becomes lost on Tatooine and must fight his way out of a deadly sandstorm! And witness Leia as she and a strikeforce of gorgeous alien commandoes storm an Imperial stonghold! This is one issue of Star Wars Tales you won't want to miss.",
